|GKB-- Living Wellspring -----------------------------------------|000

Current: |CKBChosen when cast|000
Command: |CKBwellspring <current>|000
Guild Level: 28

Living Wellspring opens a temporary spring of nwyfre inside your body.
While it lasts, it restores the chosen current every nwyfre tick.

Only one living wellspring can be open at a time.  Use it before or
during a difficult fight when you know which current you will rely on.

Example:

  |CKBwellspring marken|000
